Our goal is to exceed your expectations. Great Little Favor Co guarantees that your personalized water bottle labels will be created as you've requested, and that your purchase will arrive to you in excellent condition for your event. If you’re dissatisfied with your order for any reason, we will work together with you to make your order right.

*********************************************************************
♥ WHAT BOTTLES DO WE RECOMMEND WITH OUR LABELS ♥
*********************************************************************

When looking for a water bottle for your labels to fit your labels we recommend taking a regular piece of paper with you to the store folded 8 inches across. If the paper wraps securely around the bottle, our labels will fit that bottle.

When shopping for bottles we recommend any bottle between 8 oz to 16.9 oz such as:

Sams Club Water known as Sams Choice 10 oz bottles, 
Dasani Bottles - 16.9 and 8 oz., 
Aquafina Bottles - 16.9, 12 oz and 8 oz., and 
Nestle Bottles - 8 oz

These are a few that we've tried that fit securely with adequate overlap around the bottles. Please note that manufacturers can change their bottles without notice and due to this we highly suggest you measure the bottles prior to purchase to ensure our labels will fit whatever brand your considering purchasing.
